<br>
but i kept wondering why i found myself disliking so many minorities, yet having some good good friends who were different minorities..<br>
<br>
what i finally arrived at was i have an intense dislike for ignorant people.<br>
<br>
stupidity<br>
disabled<br>
stunted<br>
anything you can term that would mean a person is unable to excel in life.<br>
<br>
i mean i hate the black and mexican gang bangers and gang banger mentality...<br>
but i like all the professional black salereps and business men anf women i know.... at least the ones without the racist chip on their shoulder.... you know.. the ones who always make the comments about how they are discriminated against and always rush to racism as a first excuse..<br>
<br>
then again while I like my white neighbors in my upper middle class comunity, I find myself with an extreme disgust for the trailor park toothless ignorant spawns of inbreeding they show after every flood or tornado that happens.<br>
<br>
while I find asian women extremely attractive, i get disgusted by the asian women in my community that refuse to learn or speak english.. I mean you in america learn it or get the fuck out...<br>
<br>
I dont mind people who believe in god but have a good balance in their lives and are morally sound.... yet i want to punch the extremist of all cultures who want to preach at me and tell me why im going to hell if i dont donate my 14.99 or 10% or whatever it might be a week.<br>
<br>
I dont mind a little pride in your race... yet I find myself disgusted by the black power, white supremist, mecca dumbass, etc etc etc...<br>
<br>
I would almost venture to say its extremism that i hate..<br>
<br>
yet i dont hate anyone who is too rich.... or too smart.... or too strong.... or any of the other aspects that make for success in any given aspect of life..<br>
<br>
I wish there was a way that survival of the fittest would actual weed out all these fucktards a little faster. As it is it seems its multiplying on us <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
