<br>
Also, on the other hand my mother is a lesbian.  And I was raised by my lesbian mother and her girlfriend the later part of my childhood.  So discrimination/hate is a subject that hits close to home with me as well.  Thank you Ish for shining some light into the minds of the readers of this board.  Its not about race to me its about stereo typing and hate.  There are bad and good of all kinds of people.<br>
